Introducing AmeriWest Vacations.
When you book a vacation package to
Las Vegas or Reno with AmeriWest Vacations,
you get a great deal of flexibility. A great deal of
convenience. And a great deal for the money.
You see, unlike other package vacations, your
departure is not limited to certain flights
on certain days. You can book your roundtrip
on any America West flight on any day of
the week.
And your total package price will even
entitle you to triple FlightFUND^dollars on
America West's frequent flyer program
throughout 1988.
What's more, you can choose from the
finest hotels in Las Vegas and Reno. Then, with
just one phone call, you can book your
accommodations, along with air and optional
ground transportation, as little as three days
prior to departure.
Plus, in most cases, our package price is
lower than if you purchased each service
separately.
For reservations, call your Travel Agent or
AmeriWest Vacations. Were open evenings
and weekends to take your call. 1-800-356-6611.
